33:41.840 --> 33:47.620
I don't mean to be churlish about it, but it just makes a god damn much worth around here,

33:47.740 --> 33:47.900
is it?

33:48.540 --> 33:48.720
This?

33:50.300 --> 33:52.780
Well, I'll make an exception just once more.

